author: Cable The Wizard
description: A RegFox API interaction Cog, used to talk to parts of RegFox for Sekai Guild
install_msg: Installed RegFox, please set your API key, page ID, and reg URL before attempting to use any functions
end_user_data_statement: This cog stores an API key for your RegFox instance, the page ID for your RegFox page, and the link to a RegFox page. This data is stored using the RedBot config API.
